{"tid":2171849,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居民苦等11年 無探熱人流管制  康城商場開幕逼爆 恐播毒","createTime":"2020-08-24T08:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T09:05:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15b90f11adab537839cf119148cdbed8c34ebc24","tid":2171849,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/5FPWHHC2T5FGJPD2OTCYXG6PWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F5FPWHHC2T5FGJPD2OTCYXG6PWM%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzshx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=91e0adb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F5FPWHHC2T5FGJPD2OTCYXG6PWM%2F&h=923d6939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/5FPWHHC2T5FGJPD2OTCYXG6PWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n居民苦等11年 無探熱人流管制 <br />\n康城商場開幕逼爆 恐播毒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵旗下新商場「The LOHAS康城」第一期昨日開幕，首階段共13個商戶開始營業。樓盤第一期首都2009年落成至今，11年來有數萬居民入伙卻只得一間臨時超市及小量商舖，結果昨商場揭幕令區內居民蜂擁而至，逼爆商場。不過管理公司未有實施人流管制，有醫生指商場密集人流會增加傳播風險，或會成為另一波疫情爆發新群組。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：319人疑因公染疫 團體促列職業病<br />\n<br />\n康城商場首階段啟用，包括佔地逾2萬方呎的大型超級市場FRESH，以及大家樂、Pizza Hut等食肆。本報現場所見有大量人群擁至，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EQlF6K8DWWNebQBWxpbLbG-n6wE=/1968x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZTYXWSX5FF75M344DQM46HRYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEQlF6K8DWWNebQBWxpbLbG-n6wE%3D%2F1968x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZTYXWSX5FF75M344DQM46HRYE.jpg&h=a82aed3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■康城商場第一期昨日開幕，區內居民蜂擁而至，非常熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：欠應有社交距離<br />\n<br />\n本報就商場人流管制向港鐵查詢，港鐵回覆指，商場一直跟從衞生防護中心建議採取適切措施，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：明年DSE中文擬撤口試 校本評核<br />\n<br />\n對此，家庭醫生林永和表示，根據新聞照片及影片，康城商場人流太多、太密集，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林永和提醒市民，在人多地方必須時刻戴口罩，做好手部衞生，最好保持社交距離。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n日出康城首個住宅項目首都早於2009年起陸續入伙，但區內一直未有大型商場落成，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刺激本月租務成交倍升<br />\n<br />\n昨日特意前來逛街、現居將軍澳天晉的黃先生指，現場人流比想像中多，場面亦較混亂，但不擔心有播毒情況出現，「香港人都好謹慎嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n受惠商場落成效應，日出康城8月至今速錄超過140宗租務成交，較7月爆升近一倍，呎租最高見40元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Yn1uv3RXFw2CT-x6vObp6dLJZyg=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLMCL64TBVFU3I5YJSCTKNIDKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYn1uv3RXFw2CT-x6vObp6dLJZyg%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLMCL64TBVFU3I5YJSCTKNIDKQ.jpg&h=94b54b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■商場首階段共有13個商戶營業。"},{"pid":"af148595c6f6f4a9891ee67f0290e16b306640d2","tid":2171849,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"恐你老母咩 不安撚"},{"pid":"4962dba64c737e3eb8adae4f679543fb0ea6d343","tid":2171849,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"其實康城個死個英文名點讀"},{"pid":"21a5da392936018526ffa54c2598c6634c95c05f","tid":2171849,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n得藍店"},{"pid":"4aceb8bcb0c206bec100ea2771a103c416248aef","tid":2171849,"uid":9013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方都有人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}